## Personal life

Vingegaard is the son of Claus Christian Rasmussen and Karina Vingegaard Rasmussen from [Hillerslev](Hillerslev), [Thy](Thy (district)). He has one sister, Michelle Vingegaard Rasmussen. In [school](primary)(Danish Folkeskole Education), he attended Hillerslev School until [grade](7th)(Danish Folkeskole Education#Municipal folkeskole), while he took 8th and 9th grades at Tingstrup School in [Thisted](Thisted). From August 2012, Vingegaard attended the voluntary 10th grade on the cycling track at ISI Idrætsefterskole in [Ikast](Ikast). Afterwards, he enrolled in Thisted Handelsgymnasium for [education](secondary)(Secondary education in Denmark), attending the [Commercial Examination Programme](Higher)(Secondary education in Denmark#Higher Commercial Examination Programme) (HHX).

Vingegaard lives with his girlfriend Trine Marie Hansen (b. 1987) in [Glyngøre](Salling). They met when Vingegaard was a rider with [ColoQuick](Team)(Team ColoQuick) from 2016 to 2018, and Trine was the team's marketing manager. In September 2020, Trine gave birth to their daughter, Frida.
